</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="235" pageNumber="513" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="235.[1378,2584,1865,2450]" pageId="235" pageNumber="513">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1381,1728,2307,2332]" pageId="235" pageNumber="513">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Not assessed on The IUCN Red List, where itis still considered a synonymy of 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Thomas" baseAuthorityYear="1900" box="[1591,1705,2338,2371]" class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Calomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="235" pageNumber="514" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="sorella">C. sorella</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
